    "description": {
      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>These soft leather gloves are decorated with even rows of mithral rivets. Only a spellcaster with the Arcane Strike feat can activate their abilities. These abilities are as follows.   • When the wearer uses the aid another action to improve an ally's attack roll, the ally adds the wearer's Arcane Strike damage bonus to its damage roll for that attack.   • When the wearer makes an attack using Arcane Strike and hits, enemies adjacent to the target take damage equal to the wearer's Arcane Strike damage bonus. This damage is of the same type as the weapon's damage (bludgeoning, piercing, and so on).   • When the wearer uses the aid another action to improve an ally's Armor Class, the ally also adds the wearer's Arcane Strike damage bonus to his AC against the opponent.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> </p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Wondrous Item, Arcane Strike, magic weapon</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Ultimate Equipment",
